parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The warping and failure of brake rotors can cause the vehicle to vibrate or shake when braking, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Vibration or shaking of the steering wheel or entire vehicle when braking
grinding or squealing noises when applying the brakes
and difficulty stopping the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Anti-lock Braking System (ABS) can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Sudden loss of braking power
vehicle shaking or vibrating when braking
and difficulty stopping the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The shuddering or vibration of the brake pedal can cause the driver to lose control of the vehicle, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Shuddering or vibration of the brake pedal when applying the brakes
difficulty stopping the vehicle
and grinding or squealing noises when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear axle seal can cause differential oil to leak onto the rear brakes, leading to unsafe braking conditions and potential accidents.
symptoms: Rear axle seal leaking
differential oil on rear brakes
loud ticking or thumping noise from the rear end
high-pitched whine when accelerating or at high speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

difficulty shifting
loud noises or vibrations when shifting

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The shift lock handle can become stuck, making it difficult to shift gears, which can cause congestion or accidents.

difficulty shifting into park
vehicle stuck on an incline.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rear differential failure can cause the vehicle to lose power or become difficult to control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission cooler line failure can cause the transmission to overheat, leading to damage or failure, which can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
